    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/6d39369999928f0207c292915a406691.poster.avif?t=1770381299\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/6d39369999928f0207c292915a406691.webm?t=1770381299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/6d39369999928f0207c292915a406691.mp4?t=1770381299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在过去玩，然后从未来帮助自己。<br><br>Paradox！让你进行时间旅行，打破经典平台跳跃游戏的规则，创造一个充满挑战但又收获颇丰的冒险旅程，每个关卡都要玩两次：当时和现在！这将是一次充满挑战但又收获颇丰的冒险，每个关卡都要玩两次：过去和现在！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >每个关卡都玩两次！</h2><br>在第一阶段，你将扮演一位活泼的年轻教授。你的任务是收集所有散落的时间晶体，同时躲避致命的激光，穿越消失的平台，并与可能将你从现实中抹去的滴答作响的时钟赛跑。<br>似乎有人在通过操纵环境来帮助你......<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/a88fb0222e2795d1131fd3cd9248746f.poster.avif?t=1770381299\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/a88fb0222e2795d1131fd3cd9248746f.webm?t=1770381299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/a88fb0222e2795d1131fd3cd9248746f.mp4?t=1770381299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>第二阶段的转折点在于，你现在扮演年长时期、智士、特别疯狂的自己！你的任务就是操纵环境，确保青年时期的自己在这种吊诡的合作关系中取得成功。您必须引导过去时期的自己收集所有时间水晶，并在时间耗尽前完成每个关卡。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/ab4655e7cd9eed1993a39e458c4ad44b.poster.avif?t=1770381299\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/ab4655e7cd9eed1993a39e458c4ad44b.webm?t=1770381299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/ab4655e7cd9eed1993a39e458c4ad44b.mp4?t=1770381299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>注意：危险潜伏在每个角落！如果你出了差错，教授们互相碰了一下，你就会被从这个世界上抹去！幸好的是，你有一根经过改装的手杖和牛逼的滚轮，才能在无情的时间长河中获得优势。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/fa09c07527a8d1c5532876ab0813f2d7.poster.avif?t=1770381299\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/fa09c07527a8d1c5532876ab0813f2d7.webm?t=1770381299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/fa09c07527a8d1c5532876ab0813f2d7.mp4?t=1770381299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >还不确定吗？</h2><br>看看 Paradox 还准备了什么：<br><br>•\t考验脑力的关卡中布满了障碍，考验你的智慧和反应能力！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/713d1300d656781a80a5b40f9482d55d.avif?t=1770381299\" width=525 height=200 /></span><br><br>•\t专为时间旅行者准备的额外挑战和物品！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/30377fd1da847715ec48528df09ea911.avif?t=1770381299\" width=525 height=200 /></span><br><br>•\t巨大的首领迫们不及待地要把你从时间轴上抹去！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/aaef587238a260a2e56a051d0b1b2b9c.avif?t=1770381299\" width=525 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >准备好弯曲时间了吗？ </h2><br>现在就将 Paradox! 添加到你的收藏夹，随时了解我们的时间弯曲冒险！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/074b56d141f33196673b69792b1f7b71.poster.avif?t=1770381299\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/074b56d141f33196673b69792b1f7b71.webm?t=1770381299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129310/extras/074b56d141f33196673b69792b1f7b71.mp4?t=1770381299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
